    <h1 class="hero__title">Your Blueprint for Custom Excellence</h1>
    <p class="hero__text">Welcome to Cake Make, where we transform your vision into high-performance, stylish cycling apparel. Our design and production guidelines ensure that every piece we create reflects the quality and craftsmanship that define our brand.</p>
